{"tid":2211365,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「粗口大狀」馬恩國同父異母姊姊興訟 禁遺孀動用亡父遺產","createTime":"2020-09-21T05:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T08:06:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"124e5abbc06093615978305a985ad8de4a8742ae","tid":2211365,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"外號「粗口大狀」的大律師馬恩國，2015年與同父異母姊姊馬蕭蕭對簿公堂，爭奪亡父愛國畫家馬家寶的遺產。法官去年裁定馬家寶與馬蕭蕭亡母、以及與馬恩國母親的兩段婚姻皆屬有效，馬恩國母子獲判馬家寶四分之三畫作「發展權」。事隔近一年，馬蕭蕭上周再入稟高等法院，要求法庭頒令禁止馬恩國母親以遺孀身份，動用馬家寶遺產。<br />\n<br />\n根據入稟狀，原告人是馬蕭蕭，被告人是馬恩國的母親譚慧敏、即馬家寶的遺產管理人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/2AVV6K6FB5H6ROYNXO5MAGOEHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F2AVV6K6FB5H6ROYNXO5MAGOEHA%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZov2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=f95ab669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F2AVV6K6FB5H6ROYNXO5MAGOEHA%2F&h=2b731580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/2AVV6K6FB5H6ROYNXO5MAGOEHA/</a>"},{"pid":"fb79b9512d15400c61c3697d369db6298209492f","tid":2211365,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc2fc9e4da98aa38ba7d8aeb4492168388c5020","tid":2211365,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"鹿恩國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1a9cab825da360b8a446bf50b182b20734681c","tid":2211365,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"馬：fucking Chinese"},{"pid":"14657db4aa3437f1f5641cdbe3efe4a2289ec95a","tid":2211365,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"鹿思園